data.description: Discover a spacious rambler with a basement full of potential. Main Lvl is adorned with vaulted ceilings, elegant chandeliers, vast window walls, & dual-sided gas fireplace. The Kitchen gleams with SS apps, double oven, & island bar. The Living room features floating shelves. Master Suite has a ¾ Bath, dual sinks & seated shower. Bedrooms boast wood-wrapped windows, ceiling fans & built-in wardrobes. A 2-car Garage provides extra storage space & fridge. Basement w/ extra separate entry could be a potential MIL unit. Outdoors, enjoy a fenced yard, gardens, shed, patio, & RV/Boat parking. Moments to parks, schools, lakes, & I-5. No HOA!
